00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:11.640
In conclusion, the broad genomic studies reported here underscore the biological similarity

00:08:11.640 --> 00:08:14.840
of extranodal marginal zone lymphoma across anatomic sites,

00:08:14.840 --> 00:08:19.640
with potential exception of gastric extranodal marginal zone lymphoma, regardless of HPL-rate

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:20.140
