00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:25.320
This results indicate that the pathogenesis of extranodal marginal zone lymphoma

00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:29.800
is likely to be strongly influenced by the marginal zone lymphoma B cell lineage

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:34.360
than the anatomic location, even though anatomic locations may influence the composition of the

00:08:34.360 --> 00:08:39.640
tumor and microenvironment. Simultaneous mutations affecting multiple pathway

00:08:39.640 --> 00:08:44.920
